For simplicity, start with **Apache 2.0** (you can change later). But if you want BSL, use the official text from [BSL 1.1](https://mariadb.com/bsl11/). Let me know which.

Given your concern about copying, I'd suggest **BSL**. But it's heavier. For now, I'll assume **Apache 2.0** – you can always relicense later.